>How many miles do these things go before they "break". Just replaced my 
>Pertronix Ignitor which flatlined at 5.4 volts (shorted according to the 
>trouble shooting sheet)  with the original points. Only had 9000 miles on 
>it and it really provided a smoother idle to the motor with slightly 
